  "notes": [
    "Direct observer firmware for supported Wi-Fi MeshCore boards with LoRa radios.",
    "Fresh 2026-05-21 and newer images default to USA/Canada radio settings: 910.525 MHz / 62.5 kHz / SF7 / CR5.",
    "Broker slot 1 defaults to mqtt1.meshcore.ca:443/mqtt.",
    "Broker slot 2 defaults to mqtt2.meshcore.ca:443/mqtt.",
    "Use merged images for first flash or recovery.",
    "Use update images only on devices already running MeshCore.",
    "Heltec V3 is field-tested locally; expanded board targets are build-verified and should be smoke-tested over serial before broad rollout."
  ]
